<section class="dark-section py-20 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="glow-pink" style="width:400px;height:200px;background:rgba(244,63,107,0.12);top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%)"></div>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10 reveal">
    <div style="width:3px;height:48px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#f43f6b,transparent);margin:0 auto 24px"></div>
    <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light leading-relaxed" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9)">
      «وقتی ذهنت رو می‌شناسی،<br />
      <span class="font-black" style="color:#ff85a1">دیگه قربانی احساساتت نیستی.</span>»
    </blockquote>
    <p class="mt-8 text-sm" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)">تیم دوپامین سنتر</p>
  </div>
</section>
